{"title":"我们的队伍向太阳","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":11,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的队伍向太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏着祖国大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背负着民族的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是一支不可战胜的力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——题记·录《中国人民解放军进行曲》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过长夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过险峻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过崎岖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出盘陀路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一片开阔地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的队伍向太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的第三代领导带领我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一个两万五千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山，原野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沼泽，草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九百六十万平方公里版图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下我们前进的足迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星垂平野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如钓丝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钓起微明的曙色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔驰的马蹄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如急雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲打着繁花似锦的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下一路花香鸟语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下一路荫绿的火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下一路顽强的生命力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步过处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫山遍野吐红绽绿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红绿相映，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缀满大地的胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹去灾难连绵贫穷的记忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开拓出连片的繁荣和富裕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拓宽视野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重担压肩脚步阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信息时代容不得片刻观望迟疑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着昨日的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨向明天的创意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来，腾飞在创造的无限，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴，书写在每个人胸际。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代又一代接力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝聚人民的信任、信念和信心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引领我们奋勇前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步都是进行曲脚踏实地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代一个里程碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有劲挺的伟业矗天耸立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"速度，追赶着时间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无敌的英勇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——来自大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间，崛起于空间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进的胆魄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——来自大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地哺育壮志豪情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的队伍所向披靡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个高大的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连成长长的队列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疾进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着鲜血染红的地平线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着地平线半圆的旭日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猎猎，似队前飘展一面红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着党的十六大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声声欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发自巨大的胸廓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共鸣着青春壮怀激烈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看广袤的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行进着我们辉煌的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冉冉上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比壮丽……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}